// Karma Decay Function
function calculateKarmaWeight(
    uint256 karmaAmount,
    uint256 accumulationTime
) returns (uint256) {
    // Karma loses 1% per year (configurable by DAO)
    uint256 decayFactor = (block.timestamp - accumulationTime) / 365 days;
    return karmaAmount * (99 ** decayFactor) / (100 ** decayFactor);
}

// Context-Specific Karma
mapping(bytes32 => uint256) contextualKarma;
// Your karma in "Climate DAO" ‚â† karma in "Music DAO"
```

**Plus:**
- Periodic Jubilee Events (Biblical inspiration)
- Every 7 years, option for community-wide karma reset
- DAO can vote to implement

**Prevents oligarchy, enables new generations.**

